item.title: Ava's Solo SoloCast
item.description:
In this completely solitary episode of the Shut Up & Sit Down Podcast, Ava is taking you through a triplet of solo games in this meandering river of a podcast! She’s talking through Oranienburger Canal , Maquis, and Mage Knight - a smattering of solo for your Friday evening.

Have a great weekend, everybody!

item.title: Ep 45: A concrete approach to TikTok with Andrew Athias
item.description:
Today’s interview is where we go stateside as I interview Andrew Athias, who is the Digital Director for Silvi Materials in Philadelphia.  Silvi Materials is a great example of a traditional construction firm trying something different, TikTok, to market itself and it paying off. 

This interview was recorded the morning after Philadelphia’s loss in the Superbowl... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/1141325.rss
